                <p class="py-2 lg:text-base 2xl:text-xl dark:text-white dark:text-opacity-60">Unlike most software out there, Tlon is decentralized and open source. Each member accesses Tlon through their very own, unique Urbit ID, making for a truly peer-to-peer network.</p>
