                <p class="py-2 lg:text-base 2xl:text-xl dark:text-white dark:text-opacity-60">Tlon is built on Urbit, a new software stack carefully built to enable true extendability and ownership.</p>
                <p class="py-2 lg:text-base 2xl:text-xl dark:text-white dark:text-opacity-60">To use Tlon, your Urbit ID has to be online. Your Tlon account is supported by Tlon Hosting Services, which keeps your Urbit running and maintained.</p>
